statements: SELECT * FROM materials;
SELECT material_name, unit_price FROM materials WHERE material_type = 'metal';
SELECT material_id, material_name FROM materials ORDER BY unit_price DESC;
SELECT material_name, unit_price FROM materials WHERE unit_price > 50;
SELECT material_name, material_type, unit_price FROM materials WHERE unit_price < 30 ORDER BY material_name ASC;
SELECT material_name, material_type, unit_price FROM materials WHERE material_type = 'Wood';
SELECT * FROM materials WHERE unit_price > 100 ORDER BY material_name ASC;
SELECT material_name, material_type, unit_price FROM materials WHERE unit_price BETWEEN 50 AND 200 ORDER BY unit_price DESC;
SELECT material_name, material_type, unit_price FROM materials WHERE material_name LIKE 'P%' ORDER BY material_name ASC LIMIT 3;
SELECT material_name, material_type, unit_price FROM materials WHERE material_type = 'Metal' OR material_type = 'Plastic' ORDER BY material_type ASC, unit_price DESC;
SELECT * FROM filaments;
SELECT filament_name, filament_color FROM filaments WHERE filament_quantity > 10;
SELECT filament_type, filament_quantity FROM filaments ORDER BY filament_quantity DESC;
SELECT * FROM resins WHERE resin_color = 'Transparent';
SELECT resin_name, resin_quantity FROM resins WHERE resin_quantity < 50;
SELECT * FROM filaments WHERE filament_type = 'PLA' ORDER BY filament_name DESC;
SELECT filament_name, filament_color, filament_quantity FROM filaments WHERE filament_color = 'Black' AND filament_quantity > 10;
SELECT filament_type, COUNT(*) AS total_filaments FROM filaments GROUP BY filament_type HAVING total_filaments > 2;
SELECT * FROM resins WHERE resin_color = 'White' ORDER BY resin_quantity ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT resin_name, resin_type, SUM(resin_quantity) AS total_resin_quantity FROM resins GROUP BY resin_name, resin_type;
SELECT * FROM filaments;
SELECT material_name, color, quantity FROM filaments ORDER BY quantity DESC;
SELECT * FROM resins WHERE price > 50;
SELECT material_name, color, price FROM inventory WHERE type = 'resin';
SELECT inventory_id, material_name, quantity, price FROM inventory ORDER BY price DESC, quantity ASC;
SELECT * FROM filaments ORDER BY color DESC, price ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT material_name, quantity FROM resins WHERE volume > 1000;
SELECT material_name, color, SUM(quantity) as total_quantity FROM inventory GROUP BY material_name, color ORDER BY total_quantity DESC;
SELECT * FROM filaments WHERE price >= 50 AND price <= 100 ORDER BY filament_id LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM inventory WHERE type = 'plastic' OR type = 'metal' ORDER BY price DESC, quantity ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM filaments;
SELECT filament_name, quantity FROM filaments WHERE color = 'Red';
SELECT filament_name, material FROM filaments ORDER BY quantity DESC;
SELECT resin_name, quantity FROM resins WHERE cured_in_uv = TRUE;
SELECT printer_name, manufacturer, bed_size FROM printers WHERE printer_name LIKE 'Ender%';
SELECT filament_name, quantity, color FROM filaments ORDER BY filament_name DESC;
SELECT resin_name, quantity, color, cured_in_uv FROM resins WHERE quantity > 10;
SELECT printer_name, manufacturer, bed_size FROM printers WHERE manufacturer = 'Epson' OR manufacturer = 'HP';

SELECT filament_name, resins.resin_name, printers.printer_name, print_duration, print_quality FROM prints INNER JOIN filaments ON prints.filament_id = filaments.filament_id INNER JOIN resins ON prints.resin_id = resins.resin_id INNER JOIN printers ON prints.printer_id = printers.printer_id;
SELECT * FROM filaments WHERE color = 'red' AND quantity BETWEEN 20 AND 50 ORDER BY quantity ASC;
SELECT * FROM materials;
SELECT material_name, material_type FROM materials WHERE material_quantity > 0;
SELECT material_name, material_quantity FROM materials ORDER BY material_quantity DESC;
SELECT * FROM filaments WHERE filament_color = 'Black';
SELECT resin_name, resin_color FROM resins WHERE resin_color IS NOT NULL;
SELECT * FROM materials WHERE material_quantity > 100 ORDER BY material_name DESC;

SELECT materials.material_name, filaments.filament_color, resins.resin_color FROM materials JOIN filaments ON materials.material_id = filaments.filament_material_id JOIN resins ON materials.material_id = resins.resin_material_id WHERE materials.material_quantity < 50;

SELECT printers.printer_name, COUNT(print_jobs.job_id) AS total_jobs FROM printers LEFT JOIN print_jobs ON printers.printer_id = print_jobs.job_printer_id GROUP BY printers.printer_name HAVING total_jobs > 5;

SELECT materials.material_id, materials.material_name, filaments.filament_name, resins.resin_name FROM materials JOIN filaments ON materials.material_id = filaments.filament_material_id JOIN resins ON materials.material_id = resins.resin_material_id WHERE materials.material_quantity BETWEEN 50 AND 100 ORDER BY materials.material_id;
SELECT DISTINCT material_type, COUNT(*) AS total_materials FROM materials GROUP BY material_type HAVING total_materials > 1 ORDER BY total_materials DESC;
